Detailed Description

Holds the region information from region_ids.xml.

Will be empty by default. Use ServerRegionIDs if you want to read the file too.

regionGroupMap RegionIDs::m_regionGroupMap [protected]
 

The region ids for each region group.

The key value is the region_group id. The value is a pair, where the first value is a vector containing the region ids of all regions that make up the region_group, and the second value is the name or ident of the region_group

Definition at line 185 of file RegionIDs.h.

regionIDMap RegionIDs::m_regionIDMap [protected]
 

The region groups for each region id.

The key value is the region id. The value is an array containg all the ids of the region_groups that the region is a part of.
